                <h3 class="font-size-large purple weight-normal">Acceptable <span class="font-size-base gray-light italic">(readable condition)</span></h3>
                <p>All pages and the cover is intact. Pages include considerable notes in pen or highlighter, but the text is not obscured.</p>
